{"tid":1781662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯：Stand with Hong Kong People","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T14:40:10.000Z","uid":208765,"like":460,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"4418e6f94e63a2679bd2a9e4540d0fce212feb41","tid":1781662,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"港人在反送中運動中全面覺醒，除早前區議會選舉中民主派取得大勝，國際社會亦對中共魔爪日益關注。公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗日前曾到訪美國，與美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）會面，引述彭斯表明，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國人與美國政府會繼續與香港人同行（Stand with Hong Kong people）</span>。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民主派在區議會取得壓倒性優勢，美國總統特朗普亦簽署了《香港人權與民主法案》，但民主派未有停止連結國際。郭榮鏗於本月上旬曾到美國華盛頓，出席在喬治城大學舉辦講述香港社運最新情況的分享會，訪美期間他亦應美國副總統彭斯的邀請，參加在彭斯官邸舉辦的聖誕聚會。<br />\n<br />\n郭稱，席間他曾與彭斯伉儷交談，彭斯提到美國人及美國政府會繼續「Stand with Hong Kong people」。郭感謝彭斯再次表示對港人的支持外，重申國際社會支持香港爭取自由是非常重要，因為香港從來都是國際城市，強調若要外國人一方面在港投資，另一方面又要他們對香港事務噤聲是不可能的；同樣，中國一方面要利用香港的自由賺錢，另一方面又侵蝕香港的自由和法治也是不可能的。<br />\n<br />\n隨着美國制定《香港人權與民主法案》，全球多國亦開始就制裁侵犯人權者展開行動。早在上月，荷蘭國會就通過議案，訂明荷蘭政府須於明年1月底前實施荷蘭版《馬格尼茨基法案》，之後在本月初，澳洲亦將會就澳洲版《馬格尼茨基法案》進行公眾諮詢。歐盟日前亦決定啟動立法程序，準備訂立歐盟版《馬格尼茨基法案》。至於加拿大則在國會成立特別委員會去檢視中加關係，預料這有助國會向加拿大施壓，落實引用《馬格尼茨基法案》制裁打壓人權的中共與港共官員。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0d3c9f8c7fcebd821437d5ce52f3dae6c8310b","tid":1781662,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826b919d2fe7d8e68718c102835d24b2eaec161c","tid":1781662,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b479602eed36ff55faec74b01e559493e0985b","tid":1781662,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3747c1da7695fb7b17b385a5e684a00d892ef9","tid":1781662,"uid":266654,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"咁咪見到Solomon 本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 原來有美國係背後支持<br />\n感覺原來係咁正"},{"pid":"81923ce184238a4249152a9aacf241d1f083138b","tid":1781662,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35cc7cdedc1685b23ba791d50293cb01488f6871","tid":1781662,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"stand with hong kong people就徵重稅啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"cab7701c2a5e7529bfc4af75ca3f9fe8544f7424","tid":1781662,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"咁之後點 香港點做好 有無人教下"},{"pid":"3bedca51cb5318e739da92bdac390854d07ed5f7","tid":1781662,"uid":40666,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"cab7701c2a5e7529bfc4af75ca3f9fe8544f7424","tid":1781662,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"咁之後點 香港點做好 有無人教下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:32